channel.title: New Minecraft Channel!
channel.description:
Hey doods! I've recently started a Minecraft gaming channel! All support appreciated!
[url=http://www.youtube.com/hypedgamer123]HypedGamer[/url]
Please leave feedback and tell me what I could do to make these videos better :) I try to make all videos 720p HD and try to make it as fun as I can for you people to enjoy.
Thanks doods! ;D

item.title: New Minecraft Channel!
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

[quote=“Ashi, post:4, topic:547721”]I enjoyed the bad commentating!

btw why did you call brown black, peach white, etc? I don’t play minecraft, is that on purpose?[/quote]
Haha, I’d like to see you try.
And I called it that because I’m stupid and I don’t know the colours’ name :o

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:5, topic:547721”]Not my style. I have never understood what fascinates people so much just to watch others play games on youtube.
My brother watches roosterteeth all the time, constantly. For hours on end. I just don’t get how.
Wouldn’t it be more fun to, you know… Play the fucking game?[/quote]
I don’t know, I love watching people play, it’s just… I don’t know?
